social_posts.post_text:
I am so inspired by the youth of this sport.

We are hard on the gas developing a total path from the grassroots of Karting, to the grid of the #Rolex24 at Daytona. 

I am very proud to be leading the charge with support from @porschemotorsportnorthamerica. 

This photo was sent to me by a young driver who stopped by our driver lounge at the recent @superkartsusa Supernats25.  I was racing at the inaugural event in ‘98 and seeing the level of driver 25yrs on was mind blowing.  Safe to say the future is bright.

Watch this space!

@porschemotorsportnorthamerica #porschefamily

Thank you Ken Block for daring like many haven’t or wouldn’t, for inspiring generations to make your passions your work, and for co-creating brands in spaces that some might have thought didn’t exist. 

My condolences go out to his family, friends, team, teammates and so many fans. 🙏
Join us Feb 25, 2023 2pm - 7pm in Van Nuys, CA. RSVP details to come.
Employee of the month.

Great to be back with my buddy @j.bergmeister for a few days in the new #GT3RS.

Luftgekühlt 9 is about to grind into view. 

Dare I say it, but I think we have our best venue yet.  I am looking forward to the lead up with the team and reconnecting with so many friends and loyal Luft supporters. 

Wishing everyone a safe journey to SF bay. See you Saturday …and Sunday for @air__water. 

April 29-30, 2023.

A debt of gratitude /

They say it takes a village….Just over a week on from #Luft9 and the debut of @air__water leaves me reflective and thankful.  My appreciation runs deep for everyone on the internal Luft events team who shed epic proportions of effort to construct this massive production. 

I am grateful to our partners and to all who came out and brought such a showing of community and support. 

In many ways, I feel like we are just starting to hit our stride.

Porsche and Xbox have joined forces to celebrate Porsche’s 75th anniversary. 

One of the 6 iconic Porsche motorsport liveried releases is the first overall Le Mans winning 917 Salzburg design. I had the the honor to jump behind the wheel of this piece of history at this year’s 100th running of the 24h. (Swipe for pics)

————

🦅UPDATE:

What a truly overwhelming response and gift of some amazing stories.  I have read each and every entry and really loved the tales everyone has shared.  It was hard to choose just one, but I want to congratulate @kelsykate on winning this Porsche Xbox.  Your story of family, the early memories of recognizing just what makes these cars and brand so special were super inspiring, and I really hope you enjoy!

——- 

** So, here’s the scoop: they sent me two of these limited Xbox consoles and I want to send one out to a follower here.

Comment and tell me your very earliest Porsche memory. I’ll pick one of these stories  this coming Monday, Aug 28th, and drop this bad boy in the mail to the winner. 

Rules- 

1) You must have a shipping address in the USA.

2) One comment / story per follower.

@xbox @porscheusa

20 years of racing under the guidance of Alwin Springer has been quite a gift. Now it’s time to join him as co-Grand Marshals of Rennsport Reunion 7. 

I can’t wait to see so many friends and celebrate the legends and icons of this epic brand we all love.

#RR7 #porschefamily
Pops and his river-bottom boys have been hard on the prep game for this year’s #RR7 Porsche tractor race.  We are coming for you @zwart + @canepamotorsport !

Come check out my latest project car from the 1967 Sebring 12hr race and pick up yourself up a limited edition poster.  We will be at the @empi_inc @pmoinduction booth (#14) Friday at 1045am and Sunday at 1230pm.  @bentonperformance @jpgroupclassic @redcoatjames
On track. 🔥 #RR7
Live from Rennsport:  A green flag wave for the first main race of Rennsport Sunday, and a little walk around the main paddock.  #RR7

Luft’s Chattanooga gathering celebrating our hero Brian Redman, is in the books. 

@mark.pribanic’s 356A always stops people in their tracks, whether they have seen it hundreds of times or it’s their first therapy session with this frothy tub of love. 

This car speaks visually. 
Listening to it tell stories of numerous cross country trips + the connections it’s made with Mark is soo good.

Thanks to @justinbelltv for putting us together with the @chattanoogamotorcarfestival and the Defoor Brothers team on this partnership. 
What and epic part of town and a great group of folks! We’ll be back-

Image credit then_somethingnew for @luftgekuhlt

Don’t miss the action at the @mobil1 space at RADwood SoCal! 

At 2pm, meet @plmotorsport who’ll be handing out autographed, limited edition posters of the RADical #Dirtmeister  944 rally build and the #Hoonipigasus. 

Both rides will also be there in the flesh! 

BONUS: RADwood Show participants have the chance of participating in an exclusive rally led by none other than Patrick Long in the Dirtmeister. 

Tickets are still available via link in bio.
